---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The New Priesthood — The Priesthood — Nazaryah"
  description="NASA functions identically to every priesthood in history. Unquestioned interpreters. Sacred images the public cannot verify. Doctrines accepted on faith. Built by an occultist and staffed by Nazis."
>
  <div class="sw-wrap">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="sw-hero">
      <p class="sw-label">&#8213; The Priesthood &#8213;</p>
      <h1 class="sw-title">The New Priesthood</h1>
      <p class="sw-sub">
        Lab Coats Replaced Robes — The Function Is Identical
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- ── INTRO ── -->
    <section class="sw-section">
      <div class="sw-prose">
        <p>
          The third branch of the modern priesthood is the most effective because it disguises itself as the opposite of religion. NASA and the broader space establishment present themselves as the pursuit of objective truth through observation and measurement. But strip away the branding, and what remains is a system that functions identically to every priesthood in history: a class of interpreters who are not questioned, sacred images the public cannot verify, doctrines accepted on faith, and consequences for those who dissent.
        </p>
        <p>
          This page examines NASA not as a scientific agency but as a religious institution — one with occult origins, unverifiable claims, and a cosmological doctrine that directly contradicts the testimony of Scripture.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── DEEPER EXPLORATIONS ── -->
    <section class="sw-coming-section">
      <p class="sw-coming-label">&#8213; Three Studies &#8213;</p>
      <h2 class="sw-coming-title">Deeper Explorations</h2>
      <p class="sw-coming-intro">
        These three studies go beneath the institution and examine the specific claims it enforces — the cosmology it teaches, the science it invented to support it, and the invisible force it asks you to accept on faith. They fall under the New Priesthood because only a priestly system could demand this much trust in things no one can verify.
      </p>
      <div class="sw-mini-grid">

        <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood/biblical-cosmology" class="sw-mini-card">
          <span class="sw-mini-title">Cosmology</span>
          <span class="sw-mini-poetic">The Firmament</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood/gravity" class="sw-mini-card">
          <span class="sw-mini-title">Gravity</span>
          <span class="sw-mini-poetic">The Invisible Force</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood/nasa-projects" class="sw-mini-card">
          <span class="sw-mini-title">NASA Projects</span>
          <span class="sw-mini-poetic">Contradictions &amp; Cover-Ups</span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── FOUR MARKS ── -->
    <section class="sw-accordion-section">
      <p class="sw-accordion-label">&#8213; The Marks of a Priesthood &#8213;</p>
      <h2 class="sw-accordion-title">Four Marks — NASA Checks Every Box</h2>
      <p class="sw-accordion-sub">Every priesthood in history shares four features. Select each to examine how NASA matches them.</p>

      <div class="sw-accordion">

        <details class="sw-detail">
          <summary class="sw-summary"><span class="sw-part-label">Mark One</span><span class="sw-part-title">A Class of Interpreters Not to Be Questioned</span><span class="sw-chevron">+</span></summary>
          <div class="sw-body">
            <p>Astronauts, astrophysicists, and cosmologists serve as the priestly class of the modern age. Their pronouncements about the nature of the cosmos are treated as authoritative and final. The average person does not question them — not because the evidence has been personally verified, but because the institution carries an aura of unassailable credibility.</p>
            <p>This is not science. This is reverence. The same reverence the Israelites gave to the priests of Baal. The same reverence the Romans gave to the augurs who read the entrails of sacrificed animals to determine the will of the gods. The title changed. The posture of the congregation did not.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="sw-detail">
          <summary class="sw-summary"><span class="sw-part-label">Mark Two</span><span class="sw-part-title">Sacred Images the Common Person Cannot Verify</span><span class="sw-chevron">+</span></summary>
          <div class="sw-body">
            <p>Every image of the earth from space that NASA has released is, by their own admission, a composite — a digitally assembled construction, not a single photograph. The famous Blue Marble images have varied in color, continent size, and cloud patterns between versions. The Hubble deep field images, the photographs of distant galaxies, the CGI animations of spinning globes — these are the icons of the modern cosmology.</p>
            <p>They are displayed in classrooms, museums, and media as self-evident truth. But they are constructed images, accepted on faith, created by the same institution whose pronouncements you are not permitted to question. This is the exact function of sacred iconography — images that represent divine reality to the congregation, mediated through a priestly class.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="sw-detail">
          <summary class="sw-summary"><span class="sw-part-label">Mark Three</span><span class="sw-part-title">Doctrines Accepted on Faith</span><span class="sw-chevron">+</span></summary>
          <div class="sw-body">
            <p>The heliocentric model — that the earth is a spinning ball orbiting the sun at 67,000 miles per hour while the entire solar system races through the galaxy at 500,000 miles per hour — is accepted by billions of people who have never independently observed or measured any of these claims. You have never felt the earth move. You have never seen curvature with your own eyes at ground level. You accept these claims because an institution told you they are true.</p>
            <p>That is faith. The cosmologist George Ellis, writing in <em>Scientific American</em> in 1995, openly acknowledged that a model with the earth at its center could be constructed that cannot be disproved by observation alone — and that the choice between models is ultimately philosophical, not scientific. The question has never been about the data. It has always been about which authority you submit to.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="sw-detail">
          <summary class="sw-summary"><span class="sw-part-label">Mark Four</span><span class="sw-part-title">Punishment for Those Who Dissent</span><span class="sw-chevron">+</span></summary>
          <div class="sw-body">
            <p>Question the heliocentric model publicly and you will lose professional credibility, social standing, and in many cases your livelihood. Academics who express doubt are marginalized. Public figures who raise questions are ridiculed. This is not the behavior of a truth-seeking institution. This is the behavior of a religious order protecting its sacred doctrine.</p>
            <p>The inquisition did not end. It changed venues. Where the medieval church burned heretics, the modern scientific establishment cancels careers. The mechanism of punishment is different. The function — enforcing doctrinal conformity through social and professional consequences — is identical.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── DARK FOUNDATIONS LINK ── -->
    <section class="sw-report-section">
      <p class="sw-report-label">&#8213; The Historical Record &#8213;</p>
      <h2 class="sw-report-title">The Occult Origins of NASA</h2>
      <p class="sw-report-sub">
        The Jet Propulsion Laboratory was co-founded by a devoted follower of Aleister Crowley who performed daily adorations to the sun and conducted ritual sex magic. The Saturn V rocket was built by a Nazi SS officer brought to America under Operation Paperclip. The full documented report is below.
      </p>
      <a href="/sun-worship/nasa" class="sw-card sw-card-report">
        <span class="sw-card-title">Dark Foundations</span>
        <span class="sw-card-poetic">Parsons, Paperclip, and the Occult Origins of NASA</span>
        <span class="sw-card-body">Read the full report on the occultist co-founder of JPL, the Nazi SS officer behind the Saturn V, and the Masonic symbolism woven through the Apollo program.</span>
      </a>
      <p class="sw-report-note">Operation Paperclip · Jack Parsons · Freemasonry in NASA · Apollo Symbolism</p>
    </section>

    <!-- ── COSMOLOGICAL DOCTRINE ── -->
    <section class="sw-section sw-section-alt">
      <div class="sw-prose">
        <p class="sw-section-heading">The Cosmological Doctrine</p>
        <p>
          The cosmology that NASA enforces is not merely a scientific model. It is a theological claim. When you place the sun at the center of everything, you make the same declaration that Copernicus made when he called the sun the "Visible God" and invoked Hermes Trismegistus. When you reduce the earth to an insignificant speck in an incomprehensibly vast universe, you erase the biblical picture of a purposeful creation built by Yahuah as a dwelling place for man.
        </p>
        <p>
          Together, these three branches — the Sacred Art, the Institutional Church, and the Space Establishment — accomplish what no single institution could do alone: they construct an entire reality — intellectual, spiritual, and visual — that places the sun at the center and moves Yahuah's earth, Yahuah's creation, and Yahuah's people to the margins.
        </p>
        <div class="sw-scripture-block">
          <p class="sw-scripture-label">&#9656; Isaiah 66:1</p>
          <p>"Thus saith Yahuah, The heaven is my throne, and the earth is my footstool: where is the house that ye build unto me? and where is the place of my rest?"</p>
        </div>
        <p>
          The earth is the footstool of His throne. It is not an insignificant rock in a void. It is not one of trillions. It is the place Yahuah chose to put His name. And the modern priesthood has spent four centuries trying to make you forget that.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── QUOTE ── -->
    <section class="sw-footer-quote">
      <p class="sw-quote-text">"Professing themselves to be wise, they became fools, and changed the glory of the incorruptible Elohim into an image made like to corruptible man."</p>
      <p class="sw-quote-ref">— Romans 1:22&#8211;23</p>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .sw-wrap {
